{"tid":1561970,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"特朗普歡迎中國排除部分美貨關稅　指是積極姿態","createTime":"2019-09-11T23:04:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-11T23:42:48.000Z","uid":53003,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"a3fe29df5916e25ffffef0058c739edf3023ecb3","tid":1561970,"uid":53003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T23:04:55.000Z","msg":"美國總統特朗普對中國排除部分美國貨品的關稅，表示歡迎，形容中方在一場以化解全球兩大經濟體貿易戰為目標的會議舉行前，擺出「積極姿態」，亦是中方一次「重大措施」。<br />\n<br />\n特朗普說過去一年多以來，兩國針對對方的關稅措施，擾亂全球市場，他希望與中方達成貿易協議，又說自己與中方打交道，了解並喜歡對方。<br />\n<br />\n在北京，國務院關稅稅則委員會早前公布，第一批對美國加徵關稅商品的第一次排除清單，本月17日起實施。有分析指出，與已經被中方加徵關稅的5000多種美國商品比較，清單上的商品種類微不足道，但北京希望透過此舉，擺出友好姿態。不過，分析不認為今次是中美雙方已準備好達成協議的訊號。<br />\n<br />\n中美下月初在華盛頓舉行新一輪高級別經貿磋商，具體日期未確定，雙方副貿易代表，本月中先在華盛頓會晤。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1480109-20190912.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1480109-20190912.htm&d=y6uglPlKbSLkZz%2BcPL4okYoeW3mBCvqo%2FKk1k%2BmNMw8%3D&h=6d0c4b9b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1480109-20190912.htm&h=116ba129\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1480109-20190912.htm</a>"},{"pid":"5f1dfb23e12048aafca0af908460eb137062f331","tid":1561970,"uid":123991,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T23:05:14.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"72763675e23d42abc0f4e8a0d4305db0fec087dd","tid":1561970,"uid":76702,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T23:05:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2c20dfe50ea183aa81ecebb9368aa4d628ab219f","tid":1561970,"uid":42188,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T23:05:51.000Z","msg":"支那又贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2978340be2107b0d51aefdfd027ab38534fd449","tid":1561970,"uid":137725,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T23:17:17.000Z","msg":"省卻徵稅帶來嘅嘅行政費，又贏👍🏻"},{"pid":"fab90daef9f88835a16c9740a7af61050a94a044","tid":1561970,"uid":155095,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T23:27:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RrQUBgk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRrQUBgk.png&h=b5159a21&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ba988c05cd4115106e5dd6f09ab27e0a4606bd53","tid":1561970,"uid":53612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T23:42:48.000Z","msg":"去9。15 民陣 遊行<br />\n今個星期日（9月15日）係聯合國訂立的國際民主日"}]}